headline: DoorDash (DASH) Valuation Check After New OpenAI-Powered Grocery Ordering Launch
summary: DoorDash (DASH) just rolled out a grocery ordering app inside ChatGPT, letting people turn recipe ideas into near instant deliveries from local stores, and the stock quickly reacted as investors weighed what this AI partnership could mean. See our latest analysis for DoorDash. That OpenAI tie up caps a volatile stretch where sentiment has swung from worries after softer Q3 results to renewed enthusiasm, with a roughly 24 percent 1 month share price return and a powerful 3 year total...
